    {
      "id": "RV7CPKI5NW7O9",
      "title": "Good bath filter, works great",
      "body": "Cleaning up bath time has gotten a lot easier since we started using this bath filter. I was worried about all the stuff in our tap water, especially for the baby’s skin. Setting it up was a breeze, and it fits perfectly over our bathtub faucet without any extra parts. The difference is noticeable – no more harsh chlorine smell and the water just feels nicer. It has also been remarkably effective in helping relieve baby’s eczema by filtering out irritants from the water. We even set it up on subscribe and save since it’s something we want to keep using all the time. It’s been a few months and I’m glad we made the switch. Bath time is way more relaxing now and I feel better knowing the water is cleaner and gentler for the little one.",
      "rating": 5,
