      "link": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/customer-reviews/R286VQMA10CPLL/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8"
    },
    {
      "id": "R2ZLMNDTPCE9LQ",
      "title": "Love this bath filter",
      "body": "Starting to use this bath filter has made a noticeable difference in how soft the water feels during my showers at home. The installation was straightforward, and I appreciate how quickly it started working without any fuss. Living in an area with hard water, I often experienced dryness and irritation after bathing, but now my skin feels calmer and less itchy. The filter also reduces the chlorine smell, which makes shower time much more pleasant. Using it especially helps my kids’ sensitive skin feel better too. It’s a simple addition to our bathroom routine that makes a real difference in water quality.",
