    {
      "id": "R316NDKO0K34UJ",
      "title": "Bath filter works great",
      "body": "Many bath products I've tried never made much difference for my toddler's sensitive skin until we installed this bath filter. The water feels noticeably softer, which has shown significant effects in relieving baby eczema, dryness, and irritation after baths. It's especially helpful during evening baths when his skin usually gets very itchy. Since using the filter, I've seen less redness and his skin stays calmer without needing extra lotion every time. The filter is easy to set up and fits well in our bathroom. I appreciate how it gently improves bath time without adding any fuss. This has made a positive change to our nightly routine.",
