    },
    {
      "id": "R32TWJAGW6IPN3",
      "title": "Non-toxic bath filter delight",
      "body": "It hangs conveniently over the bath faucet and feels very durable with excellent quality. The multi-layer filtration system truly works—right away, I noticed the water feels softer with no lingering odor. After using it for a while, my skin feels less dry and more refreshed, and it’s definitely gentler on my hair. It’s non-toxic and provides great peace of mind, knowing it helps remove impurities and toxins, protecting the whole family. This bath water filter is absolutely amazing and incredibly easy to install, thanks to the clear instructions that made setup quick and stress-free.",
